1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,640
Si alguna vez

2
00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:01,080
habéis visto

3
00:00:01,080 --> 00:00:01,800
cosas perfectas

4
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:03,000
tiradas en la calle...

5
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:04,080
y os ha dado pena.

6
00:00:04,080 --> 00:00:04,360
Esto es

7
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,320
para vosotros.

8
00:00:05,320 --> 00:00:06,120
Pues resulta

9
00:00:06,120 --> 00:00:06,640
que cada vez

10
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:07,120
más gente

11
00:00:07,120 --> 00:00:08,040
está haciendo algo

12
00:00:08,040 --> 00:00:08,960
al respecto.

13
00:00:08,960 --> 00:00:09,840
Y funciona.

14
00:00:09,840 --> 00:00:10,520
Hoy os lo enseño

15
00:00:10,520 --> 00:00:11,480
con un ejemplo real.

16
00:00:11,480 --> 00:00:12,720
En plenas Fallas,

17
00:00:12,720 --> 00:00:13,920
la gente limpia,

18
00:00:13,920 --> 00:00:14,400
renueva,

19
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:15,720
cambia muebles...

20
00:00:15,720 --> 00:00:16,280
y hay gente

21
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:17,080
a quinientos metros

22
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:18,440
que le vendría genial.

23
00:00:18,440 --> 00:00:18,920
Y no tienen

24
00:00:18,920 --> 00:00:19,440
ni idea

25
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:19,960
de que existe.

26
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:20,720
Pues yo ya voy

27
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:21,640
preparado.

28
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,040
Lo veo,

29
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,240
lo subo a Givore,

30
00:00:23,240 --> 00:00:23,920
y en nada

31
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:24,600
alguien del barrio

32
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:25,560
lo descubre.

33
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,200
Segunda vida

34
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:26,680
para todo.

35
00:00:26,680 --> 00:00:27,040
Las calles

36
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:27,760
durante Fallas

37
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:28,640
son una mina.

38
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,680
Si no la conocéis...

39
00:00:29,680 --> 00:00:30,040
Givore.

40
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,040
Por si veis algo

41
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:31,760
esta semana.

